{"tid":1417180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武真係應該休息，再係記者會畀返個波/Deadline政府","createTime":"2019-08-05T16:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:45:42.000Z","uid":15696,"like":77,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae2a6169573e9efb8f31fba2acc0eb126744424","tid":1417180,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:07:12.000Z","msg":"- 已經近300個義士被人拉咗，好多勇武根本無論精神肉體好攰，需要休息<br />\n<br />\n- 好多人已經有少少嬲到失去理智(需要休息)，對黑警唔洗講，對其他人圍觀/非我族類都著哂火，無謂再挑起更多仇恨值<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 真係無可能「打贏」黑警，你見到幾多黑警好似我地咁爆缸? 我地不嬲只係想Be Water，玩殘黑警，而唔係不斷打仗送頭<br />\n<br />\n- !!!<strong> 和理非</strong>616之後聲音好似消失咗一樣，之前200萬人嘅震撼呢? 之前和理非勇武合作 (和理非一日&gt;設下死線-&gt;勇武一日) ，到依家出親都勇武，其實係唔理想，好多和理非已經唔敢出現<br />\n<br />\n希望個勇武可以休息吓，令個運動去返之前咁，和理非可以再一次行哂出嚟，一齊對抗呢個政府，拎返<strong>五大訴求</strong>!<br />\n<br />\nThank you!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5eeb87a28e1699393cfd9710bca70541f2ee8ee","tid":1417180,"uid":15696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"BTW機場真係一個好好嘅平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f65b04a11bf135a275581b198733a6fec00851","tid":1417180,"uid":79181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:08:43.000Z","msg":"香港示威者已經好冷靜克制 唔好自己嚇自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416511</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"621cbd131afeb820986fe2215918bf11f326ddb3","tid":1417180,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c441350d0e2429ed2a0ab335d70312174b214f33","tid":1417180,"uid":222190,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001101_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001101_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=8589bef3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001102_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001102_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=3d7f0043&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001103_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001103_72682e8336e36f0057fc85497a45fd9a.png&h=86768e47&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/06/001104_204fd6f27813ec488a814ee7dd366cf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F06%2F001104_204fd6f27813ec488a814ee7dd366cf7.png&h=64bc416f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"929533c199719d7b0785b52ababa0f48c467be23","tid":1417180,"uid":235374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:11:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察已經成為過街老鼠<br />\n下一步就要對準政權 五大訴求<br />\n要讓一班高官切身感到害怕 連記者會都唔敢出黎<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"dc92b851f191bb29950d0c2f601d40d40f3512ca","tid":1417180,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:11:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"97c9719d13800fd6ac4b34e143a40cd944832f10","tid":1417180,"uid":15696,"li